message.body: Hey Hunter want to get Indian buffet for lunch tomorrow? If not sometime this week would work as well. Just let me know.
Hey man. Ive gotta a ton of chores and running around to accomplish tomorrow. But I am slow cooking a organic grassfed chuck roast if you want to come over for dinner instead
That sounds awesome. What time and would you like me to bring or is there anything I could make?
You could bring something green . I got some artichokes I'll prolly do too but some salad or green veg would be good
Cool. What time should I come by?
